race.description: Sportsbet Same Race Multi Maiden Plate
race.comment: IN OUR HEARTS (10) missed the placings on debut two starts back then ran a better race and finished 1.75 lengths away in fifth last time out over 1100m at Bordertown. Finds a nice race and can feature in the finish. LEGAL DRAMA (7) returned from a spell two-and-a-half weeks ago when she was in the firing line on the bend before finishing sixth over this trip at Morphettville. Won't find this as tough so she will prove hard to beat. AMBUSHED (5) finished sixth at Bordertown when resuming last start, only beaten a tick under 2L Fitter this time and holds genuine claims. TUFFEN UP (11) has gone better than her form suggests in her two runs to date. Strips fitter and keeps Crowther over a longer trip. Can play a roll in the finish.
